text: Luciano Trolli (born 12 March 1904, date of death unknown) was an Italian swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre breaststroke event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Italian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Italy Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing Category:Italian male breaststroke swimmers
